## Frontend env (Vite)
#
# For local dev, you can omit these and rely on Vite's proxy:
# - frontend calls `/api/...`
# - Vite proxies `/api` -> `VITE_BACKEND_URL` (default http://localhost:3000)
#
# Optional: backend origin for Vite dev proxy
VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
#
# Optional: override API origin (useful for production builds)
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-domain.com
#
# Optional: override API prefix
# VITE_API_PREFIX=/api

